{"description":"The following synchronize block within a constructor raise a NullPointerException during the analysis with rule S3067\r\n{code}\r\nclass MyClass {\r\n  MyClass() {\r\n   synchronized (getClass()) { // Noncompliant [[sc\u003d19;ec\u003d29]] {{Synchronize on the static class name instead.}}\r\n   }\r\n}\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nWe ought to check also when synchronized block is within an initializer block.","component":"SonarJava","component_version":"4.6"}